summary: A fully animated floppy dildoswerd, or something.
descriptionHtml:
This dildoswerd is fully animated, it is pink, and translucent. It flops around as you run. It does no damage, other than the damage to your foes\' pride.

This is a proof of concept mod or something. The original idea was for my friends and I to share cracked games with this account, but it never happened. So now I am releasing the mod to the public, even though there is nothing here. It would be neat-o if someone actually made a dildo sword, though.
author: KingdomofBujee
